      "content": "I get that, but I need you to be precise. Is this a \"the database is basically wide open and can be dumped in minutes\" kind of situation, or is it more of a theoretical vulnerability that is hard to actually execute in our environment? I'm trying to gauge if the risk of an immediate exploit outweighs the guaranteed massive loss from a 6-hour outage. Give it to me straight.",
